videos.description: Tennessee's Kyle Alexander emphatically rejects Lavar Batts Jr's layup attempt at the rim.
videos.headline: Alexander denies layup attempt at the rim

videos.description: NC State big man Abdul-Malik Abu powers through the foul and gets the and-1 layup.
videos.headline: Abu finishes through contact for and-1

videos.description: Tennessee guard Jordan Bone gets the loose ball and takes it the other way for the and-1 layup at the end of the first half.
videos.headline: Tennessee turns defense into offense

videos.headline: Williams makes tough layup through contact
